#

Chickpea and Sweet Potato Buddha Bowl

$12.99
550 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh-ProteinGluten-Free

Tags:

BowlHealthyComfort FoodPlant-Based

Description

A hearty bowl of roasted sweet potatoes, protein-packed chickpeas, and fresh greens, drizzled with a creamy tahini dressing.

Ingredients

  • Chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz), rinsed and drained
  • Sweet Potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • Spinach: 2 cups, fresh
  • Tahini: 3 tablespoons
  • Lemon Juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 1 clove, minced
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Avocado: 1, sliced
  • Sesame Seeds: 1 tablespoon, for garnish
